paper_abstract: In this paper we give an algorithm for computing the higher Randic index R, of any graph. Also we compute the higher Randic index R-7 of HAC(5)C(7)[p, q] and TUZC(6)[p, q] nanotubes by GAP program.
paper_title: Computing the Higher Randic Index of HAC(5)C(7)[p,q] and TUZC(6)[p,q] Nanotubes by GAP Program
